Listener 
     ---> Selenium Event
     			----------> Click
     			----------> type
     			----------> getText
     			----------> url
     			
     			
     ---> TestNG Event
     			-----------> Test Started
     			-----------> Test End
     			-----------> Test Passed
     			-----------> Test Failed
     			-----------> Test Skipped
     			
     			

     			
To Perform above all activities we need Listeners.


Webdriver Listeners/ Selenium Listenrs - It listens to WebDriver Events
TestNG Listeners - It listens to TestNG Events



iTESTResult - It will store all the status information
ITestContext - It will store  Test Information


One single report for all our test, This test has test case name 
Our extent report get the information , we fetch all the details at run time and add accordinlgy.
For Each test method will get a dedicated name and status.
